---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Venetian Plastering in Middlesex & the Home Counties | Hancock' description='Professional venetian plastering across Middlesex and the Home Counties. Fixed-price quotes, City & Guilds certified, no subcontractors.' activePage='services'>
<section style="position:relative;height:480px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(4).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 40%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.92) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.5) 50%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 64px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/services" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Services</a> / Venetian Plastering</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,58px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Venetian Plastering</h1>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;max-width:520px;line-height:1.5;">Polished plaster for high-end interiors. Achieved by hand, not by roller. Serving Windsor, Gerrards Cross, and Ascot.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:72px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">The work</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Venetian plaster is a technique, not a product.</h2>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">True Venetian plaster — marmorino, grassello, polished plaster — requires multiple coats applied in specific sequences, each burnished at the right moisture content. The depth and lustre come from the layering process. It can't be rushed and it can't be faked.</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">We've worked on high-end properties across Windsor, Gerrards Cross, Ascot, and Beaconsfield — properties where the finish is visible and the budget reflects the standard expected.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;">
      <div style="background:#F8FAFC;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Marmorino</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Marble-powder-based plaster with a textured, stone-like finish. Warm and natural. Suits period interiors and contemporary spaces equally.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#F8FAFC;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Grassello</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Lime-based polished plaster. High gloss finish, deep lustre, smooth to the touch. The most demanding Venetian technique to apply correctly.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#F8FAFC;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Polished plaster</h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Acrylic-based system that achieves a high-sheen, marble-effect finish. More accessible price point, faster application, no less exacting in execution.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:64px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,40px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 16px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;">Discuss your Venetian plaster project.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 36px;line-height:1.65;">Fixed price agreed before work starts. We cover Windsor, Gerrards Cross, Ascot, and surrounding areas.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:07734903439" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#ffffff;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">07734 903439</a>
    </div>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:28px 0 0;">Cancellations less than 48 hours before booking incur a £100 fee.</p>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
